    "SuperCLUE-Agent foot_48 is subjected to evaluation within the Chinese context.",
    "This dataset gauges the Agent capabilities of LLMs in a Chinese context through three core abilities and ten foundational tasks, covering aspects such as tool usage, task planning, and both short-term and long-term memory.",
    "The coding evaluation datasets aim to assess the capabilities of LLMs in handling programming-related tasks, including but not limited to code interpretation, code generation, code correction, and code optimization.",
